| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3240 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4dd1070f-accd-58d6-be2a-6ed8a92362ec"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
